18 such congresses with a total of nearly 17000 delegates 
given chinas oneparty system the campaign was a placid 
affair with no debates or candidate advertisements and little 
contact between candidates and voters nominations are made chiefly 
by closeddoor committees and candidates must have good ideological 
credentials 
the law permits at most two candidates per seat but in practice 
the ratio is generally lower in the zhongnanhai district for 
example xinhua said deng and other voters were to choose two of 
three candidates 
