karpov 
the two ended the 22nd game of their chess championship series 
in a draw after the 43rd move the halfpoint each player received 
put kasparov ahead in the scheduled 24game series 1210 
the 27yearold kasparov needed a 1212 tie in the series to 
retain the title 
