their play almost amicably 
i know him he knows me kasparov said in an interview 
you have to realize he is the only serious opponent for me i am 
talking chess with the no two in the world 
kasparov is the highestrated player in the history of the 
sport with 2800 points in rating chess grandmasters the previous 
best was 2785 by american chess genius bobby fischer who held the 
world title from 1972 until he refused to defend it in 1975 that 
allowed karpov to take it until kasparaov came along 
