three weeks wednesday rising above 27 a barrel on increasing 
fears of a middle east war 
contracts for home heating oil unleaded gasoline and natural 
gas also rose sharply in subdued new york mercantile exchange 
trading after a fourday christmas weekend 
light sweet crude oil for february delivery increased 130 to 
2722 per 42gallon barrel it was the biggest singleday gain 
since a 151 per barrel jump dec 4 
